    <h3>Inspection Rules</h3>
    <p>In order for an inspection to be required for a hydrant the following conditions must apply.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Hydrant Status -> Active</li>
        <li>Hydrant Billing -> Public</li>
        <li>Has no inspections</li>
        <li>
            Inspection Frequency - A valid inspection has not been performed within the hydrant's specified frequency.
            E.g. 3 months
        </li>
    </ul>

