    <h3>Out of Service</h3>
    <p>
        Use the "Out of Service" tab to call a hydrant out of service or back into service.
    </p>
    <p>
        Notifications will be sent to any users that are signed up to receive them. They will
        receive a notification when a hydrant is called out of service and back into service.
        In addition a town can be setup to receive a notification as well. This is done by adding
        a town contact with the contact type of "Hydrant Out Of Service".
